MPI CORP (6223)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 17.20% to NT$288,633,000 from NT$348,605,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            288,633          348,605    
YOY%             -17.20%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,222,435        2,090,185   
YOY%             -41.52% 
=================================================================
 